  "texts": [
    "So we can safely conclude from the graph that our proposed model effectively classifies any instance present in our dataset.",
    "Anovel CNN based lightweight model for COVID-19 detection from CXR scans is proposed in this paper.",
    "The model has 83,307 parameters, 81,647 of which are trainable and 1660 of which are not.",
    "The dataset used consisted of 21,165 CXR images with each image of 299*299 pixel.",
    "The images are divided into four categories: normal, lung opacity, viral pneumonia, and COVID-19."
